      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Residual norms must converge below 1e-6 for all load steps; energy balance must be confirmed.",
      "rationale": "All nonlinear load steps converged with force residual norms below 1e-7. Energy balance was confirmed at each increment. No spurious hourglassing detected. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
