      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation workflow must be executed by trained analysts following a documented simulation plan reviewed by an independent engineer.",
      "rationale": "The FEA workflow was executed by two independent analysts following a pre-approved simulation plan. An independent senior engineer reviewed boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions prior to result extraction. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
