    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted because the overall credibility margin is positive, the F1717 protocol is FDA-recognized, and the E/uval metric confirms model accuracy across all three QoIs within pre-specified bounds. The package is submitted under ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be appended prior to regulatory submission.",
